This page on SteamDB lists all the games tagged as 'Education' on Steam. The 'Education' tag is applied to games that are designed to teach various concepts, skills, or subjects in an engaging and interactive way. These games can range from simulators that model real-world phenomena to educational software aimed at children. The list is updated automatically, ensuring users have access to the most current information about these games. Whether you're a student looking for an alternative learning tool, a teacher seeking supplemental materials, or simply curious, this page offers a wealth of educational gaming options.
